Played this game for 2hr on Steam, 2hr on Switch and 9hr on Xbox and I noticed something that it feels wrong, You can't account sync in between platforms ;-;
I have grind for the same skin 3 times because there is no account sync in between platforms even if you linked your Bandai Namco Id, you cant even played the same account you last played on,
 I think we need a account sync feature if you link your Bandai Namco id so we can enjoy our stuff we got on PlayStation, Xbox, Switch and Steam because it's a big in the ass to grind 3 different accounts on 3 separate platform despise being on the same Bandai Namco Id
